          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4770">
            <h1 id="director-general-borders-immigration-and-citizenship-systems-policy-and-strategy-group">Director General, Borders, Immigration and Citizenship Systems Policy and Strategy Group </h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Border, Immigration and Citizenship System (BICS) is made up of Border Force, Her Majestyâ€™s Passport Office, Immigration Enforcement, UK Visas and Immigration and BICS Policy and Strategy Group (PSG), which provides the policy and strategic structure which underpins the rest of the system.</p>

<p>BICS PSG supports the delivery of the 5 BICS priorities agreed with ministers:</p>

<ul>
  <li>managing the implications of Brexit</li>
  <li>securing the border</li>
  <li>reducing the illegal migrant population</li>
  <li>providing world class services and creating prosperity</li>
  <li>protecting vulnerable people and communities</li>
</ul>

